    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this absolute gem. It\u2019s in such incredible, pristine condition\u2014honestly, it\u2019s like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it still has that new-car feel that\u2019s so hard to find. It drives like a total dream and looks stunning from every angle. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
