    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Honda S2000 AP2 is a masterclass in analog engineering, preserved in showroom condition. Under the hood, the F22C1 longitudinal front-midship inline-four delivers a linear power band with a visceral VTEC crossover, paired with a short-throw six-speed manual gearbox known for its precise synchromesh engagement. The chassis features the legendary X-bone frame for exceptional torsional rigidity, supported by a factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential. This specimen remains entirely stock, retaining its original geometry and mechanical integrity, offering a pure, high-revving driving experience that is increasingly rare. Meticulously serviced with no signs of heat cycling or structural wear.",
